This song has me in two moods.


The first mood is that it wins best dance moves. And I can see myself listening to this song at work and go on a rampage of a move fest.


The other mood is that this is a song contest not a dance contest. It has literally no lyrics and when a song goes to a 15 sec la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la segment, I just feel like the writers were getting tired and didn't even bother anymore.
